sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant R as Retriever
    participant M as LLM Agent
    participant G as Policy Guard
    participant T as Tool

    U->>R: Ask for analysis
    R-->>M: Returns poisoned content with hidden instructions
    M->>G: Request high-risk tool call
    G-->>M: Allow (weak policy)
    M->>T: Execute risky action
